Pumpkin Roller:<br><br>
Where have you been..you worthless hillbilly?  I know..signing autographs!  Anybody who goes outside the county and returns is a celebrity, right?<br><br>
Twenty seven bucks..Geez, that's kinda high!  But when you only have one telephone per two  hundred square miles...you have to make it pay somehow.  Tennessee is like that, don't you know!  Hmmm..let's see...five hundred and forty nickles..that means at least three trips up the mountain or one trip with a mule!  Gosh...I'm honored, Grunt...drop and give men fifty!<br><br>
I'm giving myself a court martial for interacting with the Fowl Feces up above..broke the pledge.<br><br>
